<ptxt>INSPECT FLUID LEVEL IN RESERVOIR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Inspect the fluid level.</ptxt>
<ptxt>If brake fluid level is lowered, check for leakage and inspect the disc brake pad. If necessary, refill the reservoir with brake fluid after repair and replacement.</ptxt>
